    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and entirely free of creases or wear. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with factory precision, supported by a meticulous, fully documented service history. This isn't just a used car\u2014it's a time capsule. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover, non-smoker owned, and never driven in inclement weather. It is, quite simply, as close to new as a pre-owned vehicle can get.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects an uncompromising commitment to excellence, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this unit has been rigorously vetted to ensure it meets the highest standards of quality and performance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark example for the most sophisticated collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you\u2019d think this beauty just rolled off the showroom floor today! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and still has that wonderful new-car smell. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 era. Meticulously maintained, the powerplant features individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile six-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise lateral dynamics. All mechanical components are in peak operational condition, including proactive rod bearing replacement and a pristine subframe. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, with no evidence of thermal cycling wear or fluid perspiration throughout the drivetrain. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the serious purist.",
